1. Configuration

  The installation  paths  can  be  configured  in  the  makefile
  "in.mk".  There are three paths configureable:

     INCDIR   Directory for include files
     LIBDIR   Directory for library files
     MANDIR   Directory for man pages


2. Installation

  The library is build with the command

     $ make

  Installation usually has to be done as root:

     # make install

  Generated files are removed with:

     $ make clean


3. Deinstallation

  Deinstallation is done as root with

     # make uninstall
